Jabber Host

Copyright 2011 Opt-In Software.
http://www.optinsoft.com/

This program allows to extract forgotten jabber password from your jabber client.
I wrote this program for myself when I forgot my jabber password and extracted it from Miranda IM.

Read more about usage of this program here:
http://www.optinsoft.com/miranda-jabber-password-recovery.php

To build Jabber Host from sources you will need Delphi 7 with Indy 9 library.

You can freely use this program and code for your needs